{"tid":504012,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[Android] 煮咗未 - 比你地屋企賓賓印印的食譜app","createTime":"2017-12-19T12:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T11:22:41.000Z","uid":19521,"like":11,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa091735f5890f94e19bfba4dd55b5ec39a7160","tid":504012,"uid":19521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"我哋又寫咗隻新app，事源見到太多新穎暗黑料理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，令到我哋有新 ge idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSource : 蘋果日報 -【女傭暗黑料理】麥樂雞煲湯/番茄薯條湯　你中過伏未？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/food/daily/article/20171002/20169964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ffood%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171002%2F20169964&d=FWXRXA3W5kmi1UuwQ2ATiviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5519f2b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ffood%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171002%2F20169964&h=fa89fd81\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/food/daily/article/20171002/20169964</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下幫唔幫到大家手同賓賓印印講清楚想食啲咩，因為隻 app 有大量翻譯咗做中、英、菲律賓同印尼文ge食譜，你地揾到啱心水ge食譜，仲可以即刻轉咗工人識睇ge語言，開心share比佢地，想知點用就 click 下面條 link 睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 百屌成材，巴絲打埋嚟俾意見我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時都只得 An機 可以用，iOS 就睇大家反應先...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.slashhh.cookjormaid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.slashhh.cookjormaid&d=F